@startuml US-07
title US-07 View Order History

actor User
boundary "Web UI" as UI
control "OrderController" as OC
control "OrderService" as OS
database "OrderRepository" as OR

User -> UI: Go to "My Orders"
UI -> OC: GET /users/{userId}/orders
OC -> OS: getOrderHistory(userId)
OS -> OR: findByUserId(userId)
OR --> OS: orders(orderDate, totalAmount, orderId)
OS --> OC: orders
OC --> UI: 200 OK + list
UI --> User: Render orders list
@enduml
